statements.sql: select `category`.* from `category` inner join `products` on `products`.`category_id` = `category`.`id` inner join `product_variations` on `product_variations`.`product_id` = `products`.`id` where `category`.`status` = 'AC' and `products`.`status` = 'AC' and `product_variations`.`status` = 'AC' group by `category`.`id`

select `products`.*, COALESCE(cart.quantity,0) as cart_quantity, COALESCE(cart.id,0) as cart_id, IF ((select count(favourite_products.product_id) from favourite_products where favourite_products.product_id = products.id and favourite_products.user_id='1' and favourite_products.status='AC') > 0,'Favourites_selected.png','Favourites.png') as favourite, (select product_variations.price from product_variations where product_variations.product_id = products.id and product_variations.status='AC' limit 1) as price, (select product_variations.weight from product_variations where product_variations.product_id = products.id and product_variations.status='AC' limit 1) as weight, (select product_units.name from product_variations join product_units on product_variations.unit_id = product_units.id where product_variations.product_id = products.id and product_variations.status='AC' and product_units.status='AC' limit 1) as unit, (select product_variations.special_price from product_variations where product_variations.product_id = products.id and product_variations.status='AC' limit 1) as special_price, (select round((product_variations.price - product_variations.special_price)*100 / product_variations.price) from product_variations where product_variations.product_id = products.id and product_variations.status='AC' limit 1) as discount from `products` inner join `product_variations` on `product_variations`.`product_id` = `products`.`id` left join `cart` on `cart`.`product_id` = `products`.`id` and (`cart`.`user_id` = 1 and `cart`.`status` = 'AC') where (`products`.`status` = 'AC' and `is_featured` = 1 and `product_variations`.`status` = 'AC') group by `products`.`id`
